 before marriage, visit records, photos, and explanation of relationship development."},{"level":2,"question":"Canada – Spouse / Partner Sponsorship workflow — best practice for client question: Does sponsor need minimum income:","options":["Spousal sponsorship generally has no LICO requirement for spouse/partner/child, but sponsor must not be on social assistance (except disability) and must meet …","Family class sponsorship allowing a Canadian citizen or permanent resident to sponsor a spouse, common-law, or conjugal partner for permanent residence. Outlan…","Legally married or qualifying common-law/conjugal relationship · Sponsor meets income/residency requirements · Genuine relationship · Medical and security clea…","Outland: partner outside Canada, can visit during processing. Inland: partner in Canada; may qualify for open work permit while awaiting decision."],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Spousal sponsorship generally has no LICO requirement for spouse/partner/child, but sponsor must not be on social assistance (except disability) and must meet undertaking obligations."},{"level":2,"question":"In the Canada – Spouse / Partner Sponsorship process, what is the correct approach to client question: What happens after refusal?","options":["Review refusal letter carefully. Options may include appeal (IAD) for in-Canada refusals in some cases, or reapplication with stronger evidence.","Family class sponsorship allowing a Canadian citizen or permanent resident to sponsor a spouse, common-law, or conjugal partner for permanent residence. Outlan…","Legally married or qualifying common-law/conjugal relationship · Sponsor meets income/residency requirements · Genuine relationship · Medical and security clea…","Outland: partner outside Canada, can visit during processing. Inland: partner in Canada; may qualify for open work permit while awaiting decision."],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Review refusal letter carefully. Options may include appeal (IAD) for in-Canada r