l does not guarantee invitation. CRS cutoffs vary per draw. PNP can add 600 points.","warning":true},{"label":"Key authority","value":"Immigration, Refugees and Citizenship Canada (IRCC)"},{"label":"After approval","value":"COPR issued; complete landing; apply for PR card. Meet residency obligations for citizenship pathway."}],"eligibility":[{"criterion":"Eligible program (FSW/CEC/FST)","met":true},{"criterion":"Language test (CLB minimum per program)","met":true},{"criterion":"ECA for foreign credentials (FSW)","met":true,"note":"WES/IQAS etc."},{"criterion":"CRS score competitive for recent draws","met":false,"note":"Assess against recent cutoffs"},{"criterion":"Work experience documented (NOC/TEER)","met":true},{"criterion":"Proof of funds (FSW/ FST if applicable)","met":true},{"criterion":"Medical and police completed after ITA","met":false}],"redFlagsBanner":"Without ITA, do not submit PR application. Improve CRS via language retake, ECA, PNP, or Canadian experience before expecting invitation.","redFlags":[{"title":"CRS below recent draw cutoffs","description":"Client expects ITA with non-competitive score.","fix":"Retake language for higher CLB; pursue PNP; gain Canadian work experience","severity":"Very common"},{"title":"Wrong NOC/TEER code","description":"Work experience coded incorrectly affecting points.","fix":"Verify TEER category against official duties and reference letters","severity":"Very common"},{"title":"Reference letter deficiencies","description":"Employer letters missing duties, hours, or dates.","fix":"Detailed reference on company letterhead matching NOC duties","severity":"Common"},{"title":"ECA not completed","description":"Foreign degree not assessed before profile.","fix":"Complete ECA from designated organisation","severity":"Common"},{"title":"Language scores expired","description":"IELTS/CELPIP older than 2 years at ITA.","fix":"Retake before accepting ITA if expiring","severity":"High"},{"title":"Misrepresentation risk","description":"Inflated experience or false documents.","fix":"Honest accurate profile—misrepresentation has permanent consequences","severity":"High"}],"faqs":[{"q":"Can we guarantee ITA or PR?","a":"No. CRS cutoffs change each draw. We improve profile quality but never promise ITA or approval."},{"q":"What CRS score needed?","a":"Varies each draw—check recent IRCC draw results. Category-based draws have different cutoffs."},{"q":"How to improve CRS?","a":"Higher language scores, additional education ECA, Canadian work experience, PNP nomination (+600), French language bonus."},{"q":"What is PNP?","a":"Provincial Nominee Program—province nomination adds 600 CRS points, virtually ensuring ITA."},{"q":"Processing after ITA?","a":"Typically 6 months standard for most EE applications—verify current IRCC processing times."},{"q":"Can spouse be included?","a":"Yes—spouse factors into CRS; include if beneficial to score."},{"q":"Proof of funds when?","a":"Required at ITA stage for FSW; amount per family size on canada.ca."},{"q":"What if ITA declined?","a":"Profile may re-enter pool if valid—assess options carefully."},{"q":"What is Description for this service?","a":"Federal economic immigration system managing FSW, CEC, and FST programs. Candidates create profile, receive CRS score, and apply for PR if invited (ITA)."},{"q":"What is Eligible applicants for this service?","a":"Meet FSW/CEC/FST criteria · Valid language tests · ECA for foreign education · Sufficient CRS score · Medical and police clearances"},{"q":"What is ITA not guaranteed for this service?","a":"Profile in pool does not guarantee invitation. CRS cutoffs vary per draw. PNP can add 600 points."},{"q":"Important note on ITA not guaranteed?","a":"Profile in pool does not guarantee invitation. CRS cutoffs vary per draw. PNP can add 600 points."},{"q":"What is Key authority for this service?","a":"Immigration, Refugees and Citizenship Canada (IRCC)"},{"q":"What is After approval for this service?","a":"COPR issued; complete landing; apply for PR card. Meet residency obligations for citizenship pathway."},{"q":"Is Eligible program (FSW/CEC/FST) required?","a":"Eligible program (FSW/CEC/FST) is typically required."},{"q":"Is Language test (CLB minimum per program) required?","a":"Language test (CLB minimum per program) is typically required."},{"q":"Is ECA for foreign credentials (FSW) required?","a":"WES/IQAS etc."},{"q":"Is CRS score competitive for recent draws required?","a":"Assess against recent cutoffs"},{"q":"Is Work experience documented (NOC/TEER) required?","a":"Work experience documented (NOC/TEER) is typically required."},{"q":"Is Proof of funds (FSW/ FST if applicable) required?","a":"Proof of funds (FSW/ FST if applicable) is typically required."},{"q":"Is Medical and police completed after ITA required?","a":"Assess whether Medical and police completed after ITA is satisfied for this case."},{"q":"What is the Processing time?","a":"6–12m — After ITA received"},{"q":"What is the Government fee?","a":"CAD $1,525+ — PR application after ITA"},{"q":"What is the Our approval rate?","a":"94% — ~88% post-ITA benchmark"},{"q":"What is the Required docs?","a":"16 — + ECA, language, work ref"},{"q":"What is the Consultancy fee?","a":"See fee tab — + govt & ECA/tests"},{"q":"What if the client has CRS below recent draw cutoffs?","a":"Retake language for higher CLB; pursue PNP; gain Canadian work experience"},{"q":"Why is CRS below recent draw cutoffs a problem?","a":"Client expects ITA with non-competitive score."},{"q":"What if the client has Wrong NOC/TEER code?","a":"Verify TEER category against official duties and reference letters"},{"q":"Why is Wrong NOC/TEER code a problem?","a":"Work experience coded incorrectly affecting points."}],"compliance":["Client service agreement and consent must be on file before submission","Never guarantee visa or immigration approval; use approved-language only","Fee quotes must separate consultancy, government, and third-party costs","Paid RCIC representation requires valid CICC membership"],"proTips":["Calculate CRS at intake with official calculator","Verify TEER codes against NOC 2021","Secure detailed employer reference letters early","Monitor draw trends—set realistic expectations","PNP exploration if CRS below cutoff"],"postApproval":["Send COPR and landing checklist","Explain PR card application","Remind residency days for citizenship","Connect to settlement services"],"performance":{"ourRate":94,"industryRate":88,"stats":[{"label":"Files this year","value":"89"},{"label":"Approved","value":"84"},{"label":"Refused","value":"3"},{"label":"Withdrawn","value":"2"}]},"approvalFactors":[{"label":"Post-ITA approval","ours":94,"benchmark":88},{"label":"CRS assessment accuracy","ours":91,"benchmark":75},{"label":"Reference letter quality","ours":88,"benchmark":72},{"label":"First-submit completeness","ours":93,"benchmark":80}],"timeline":[{"weeks":"1–4","title":"CRS assessment, ECA, language tests"},{"weeks":"4–6","title":"Profile creation and pool entry"},{"weeks":"Variable","title":"Wait for ITA (CRS-dependent)"},{"weeks":"6–12m","title":"PR application processing after ITA"}],"relatedServices":[{"label":"Canada – PGWP","libraryId":""},{"label":"Canada – Work Permit","libraryId":""},{"label":"Canada – Spouse Visa","libraryId":""}],"changelog":[{"version":"v2.0","date":"7 Jun 2026","author":"Service Library","summary":"Expanded FAQs to 30 counselor Q&A pairs."},{"version":"v2.0","date":"6 Jun 2026","author":"Service Library","summary":"Added 75 levelled quiz questions (Level 1–3, 25+ each) and expanded counselor content."},{"version":"v1.0","date":"6 Jun 2026","author":"Service Library","summary":"Initial Express Entry PR counselor content."}],"staffNotes":[{"author":"Documentation team","date":"6 Jun 2026","text":"Never collect full PR fee before ITA—profile setup fee only until invitation received."}],"resources":[{"title":"IRCC — Express Entry","url":"https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees