 DLI program is typically required."},{"q":"Is Valid study permit at completion required?","a":"Valid study permit at completion is typically required."},{"q":"Is Completion letter / transcript required?","a":"Completion letter / transcript is typically required."},{"q":"Is Applied within 180 days of completion required?","a":"Critical deadline"},{"q":"Is Full-time student status maintained required?","a":"Full-time student status maintained is typically required."},{"q":"Is Passport valid through desired PGWP period required?","a":"Passport valid through desired PGWP period is typically required."},{"q":"Is Not previously received PGWP required?","a":"One-time rule"},{"q":"What is the Processing time?","a":"3–5m — Online application"},{"q":"What is the Government fee?","a":"CAD $255 — Verify on canada.ca"},{"q":"What is the Our approval rate?","a":"92% — ~85% benchmark"},{"q":"What is the Required docs?","a":"8 — + completion letter"},{"q":"What is the Consultancy fee?","a":"See fee tab — + govt only"},{"q":"What if the client has Applied after 180-day deadline?","a":"Apply within 180 days or restore status if eligible"},{"q":"Why is Applied after 180-day deadline a problem?","a":"Completion letter date exceeded 180 days."},{"q":"What if the client has Program too short?","a":"Verify eligibility before completion; plan alternative"},{"q":"Why is Program too short a problem?","a":"Program under 8 months generally ineligible."}],"compliance":["Client service agreement and consent must be on file before submission","Never guarantee visa or immigration approval; use approved-language only","Fee quotes must separate consultancy, government, and third-party costs"],"proTips":["Confirm PGWP eligibility at enrolment stage not just graduation","Apply within 180 days of completion letter","Renew passport if expiring soon","Obtain official completion letter from DLI","Track implied status work rules if applying near permit expiry"],"postApproval":["Send PGWP approval and expi