no proof of UK address.","fix":"Tenancy agreement, council tax, photos of property","severity":"Common"},{"title":"English requirement missed","description":"No A1 SELT when required.","fix":"Book UKVI-approved SELT early","severity":"Common"},{"title":"Prior refusals undisclosed","description":"Hidden UK or immigration refusals.","fix":"Full disclosure with changed circumstances","severity":"High"}],"faqs":[{"q":"Can we guarantee spouse visa approval?","a":"No. UKVI assesses financial, relationship, and eligibility criteria. Genuine marriages can still face refusals if evidence is weak."},{"q":"What is minimum income requirement?","a":"Threshold changes with policy—verify current amount on gov.uk Appendix FM. Can combine salaried/non-salaried income or use savings alternative."},{"q":"Can savings substitute income?","a":"Yes, if meeting specified savings amount held for required period. Calculate per gov.uk guidance."},{"q":"How long until ILR?","a":"Typically 5 years on spouse route (with extensions). Verify current ILR rules and English requirements at each stage."},{"q":"Can spouse work in UK?","a":"Yes, generally no work restrictions on spouse visa—verify conditions on grant letter."},{"q":"Is marriage in India recognised?","a":"Yes if legally valid. Provide marriage certificate; certified translation if not in English."},{"q":"What if sponsor is on benefits?","a":"Some benefits count toward income; others don''t. Check permitted income sources on gov.uk."},{"q":"TB test required?","a":"Yes for Indian applicants from approved clinic before application."},{"q":"What is Description for this service?","a":"Family visa for spouse, civil partner, or unmarried partner of British citizen or person with settled/pre-settled status in UK. Leads to ILR pathway after qualifying period."},{"q":"What is Eligible applicants for this service?","a":"Valid marriage/civil partnership or 2+ years cohabitation · Sponsor meets financial requirement · Adequate accommodation · English A1 (entry) · Genuine relationship"},{"q":"What is Financial requirement for this service?","a":"Sponsor must meet minimum income threshold or qualify via savings. Rules updated periodically—verify current threshold on gov.uk."},{"q":"Important note on Financial requirement?","a":"Sponsor must meet minimum income threshold or qualify via savings. Rules updated periodically—verify current threshold on gov.uk."},{"q":"What is Key authority for this service?","a":"UK Visas and Immigration (UKVI) — Home Office"},{"q":"What is After approval for this service?","a":"Initial visa typically 33 months (if applying from outside UK); extension and ILR pathway. Maintain genuine relationship and comply with conditions."},{"q":"Is Sponsor is British citizen or settled/pre-settled required?","a":"Sponsor is British citizen or settled/pre-settled is typically required."},{"q":"Is Valid marriage or qualifying relationship required?","a":"Marriage cert or 2+ years cohabitation proof"},{"q":"Is Financial requirement met required?","a":"Income or savings per Appendix FM"},{"q":"Is Adequate accommodation in UK required?","a":"Tenancy or ownership evidence"},{"q":"Is English A1 (entry clearance) required?","a":"SELT or exempt nationality"},{"q":"Is TB test (if from listed country) required?","a":"India requires approved clinic test"},{"q":"Is Genuine relationship evidence required?","a":"Genuine relationship evidence is typically required."},{"q":"What is the Processing time?","a":"12–24w — Outside UK entry clearance"},{"q":"What is the Government fee?","a":"£1,846 — + IHS (5 years typical)"},{"q":"What is the Our approval rate?","a":"90% — ~80% industry benchmark"},{"q":"What is the Required docs?","a":"19 — + financial & relationship"},{"q":"What is the Consultancy fee?","a":"See fee tab — + govt & IHS"},{"q":"What if the client has Financial requirement not met?","a":"Calculate on gov.uk; combine permitted income sources or use savings route"},{"q":"Why is Financial requirement not met a problem?","a":"Sponsor income below threshold without qualifying savings."},{"q":"What if the client has Weak relationship evidence?","a":"Chronological relationship narrative; communication logs; visit evidence"},{"q":"Why is Weak relationship evidence a problem?","a":"Few photos, no cohabitation proof, inconsistent timeline."}],"compliance":["Complex cases may need immigration solicitor—refer when appropriate","Never guarantee visa approval","Client must provide truthful relationship and financial evidence","Separate consultancy, UKVI, IHS fees in quotes"],"proTips":["Calculate financial requirement at intake before fee collection","Build relationship timeline document from first meeting","Collect UK accommodation evidence early from sponsor","Book A1 SELT for beneficiary in parallel with document prep","Pay IHS using gov.uk calculator—save receipt"],"postApproval":["Explain visa validity and BRP/collection if applicable","Remind on extension timeline before expiry","Guide on English requirements for ILR pathway","Connect to UK settlement briefing if offered"],"performance":{"ourRate":90,"industryRate":80,"stats":[{"label":"Files this year","value":"41"},{"label":"Approved","value":"37"},{"label":"Refused","value":"3"},{"label":"Withdrawn","value":"1"}]},"approvalFactors":[{"label":"Our rate vs industry","ours":90,"benchmark":80},{"label":"Financial compliance","ours":88,"benchmark":72},{"label":"Relationship evidence","ours":86,"benchmark":74},{"label":"First-submit completeness","ours":92,"benchmark":76}],"timeline":[{"weeks":"1–2","title":"Eligibility, financial calc, fee agreement"},{"weeks":"2–6","title":"Relationship & financial document collection"},{"weeks":"6–8","title":"TB test, SELT, IHS payment, submission"},{"weeks":"8–10","title":"Biometrics at VAC"},{"weeks":"12–24","title":"UKVI processing"}],"relatedServices":[{"label":"UK – Skilled Worker","libraryId":""},{"label":"UK – Visitor Visa","libraryId":""},{"label":"UK – Graduate Route","libraryId":