":"Medium"}],"faqs":[{"q":"Can we guarantee visitor visa approval?","a":"No. Home Affairs decides each case. We improve documentation but never promise approval."},{"q":"Which stream for family visit?","a":"Sponsored Family stream if eligible with eligible sponsor in Australia; otherwise Tourist stream with invitation."},{"q":"How much funds to show?","a":"Enough for flights, accommodation, and daily expenses for planned stay. No fixed amount—must be credible."},{"q":"Can visitor work?","a":"No paid work. Limited business visitor activities only on appropriate stream."},{"q":"Can visitor switch to student visa in Australia?","a":"Generally must apply from outside Australia for student visa—verify current rules."},{"q":"Does prior refusal affect reapplication?","a":"Must disclose. Success requires materially improved circumstances."},{"q":"Is health exam required?","a":"Depends on profile and stay—follow Home Affairs health requirements."},{"q":"How long can visitor stay?","a":"Officer grants stay period—often up to 3, 6, or 12 months depending on stream and case."},{"q":"What is Description for this service?","a":"Subclass 600 visitor visa for tourism, visiting family, or short business visits to Australia. Applied online via ImmiAccount with stream selection."},{"q":"What is Eligible applicants for this service?","a":"Temporary visit purpose · Funds for stay · Strong ties to India · Genuine intention to depart · Health and character requirements"},{"q":"What is Stream selection for this service?","a":"Tourist, Sponsored Family, Business Visitor streams have different evidence needs. Choose correctly at application."},{"q":"Important note on Stream selection?","a":"Tourist, Sponsored Family, Business Visitor streams have different evidence needs. Choose correctly at application."},{"q":"What is Key authority for this service?","a":"Department of Home Affairs (Australia)"},{"q":"What is After approval for this service?","a":"Respect stay period and visa conditions. No work except limited business visitor activities. Overstay affects future visas."},{"q":"Is Valid passport required?","a":"Valid passport is typically required."},{"q":"Is Clear temporary visit purpose required?","a":"Clear temporary visit purpose is typically required."},{"q":"Is Proof of funds required?","a":"Cover trip and stay costs"},{"q":"Is Strong ties to India required?","a":"Employment, business, family, property"},{"q":"Is Health insurance recommended required?","a":"Health insurance recommended is typically required."},{"q":"Is Biometrics (if requested) required?","a":"Assess whether Biometrics (if requested) is satisfied for this case."},{"q":"Is Immigration history disclosed required?","a":"Immigration history disclosed is typically required."},{"q":"What is the Processing time?","a":"2–6w — Stream-dependent"},{"q":"What is the Government fee?","a":"AUD $195 — Tourist stream approx"},{"q":"What is the Our approval rate?","a":"71% — ~59% industry benchmark"},{"q":"What is the Required docs?","a":"9 — + invitation if applicable"},{"q":"What is the Consultancy fee?","a":"See fee tab — + govt only"},{"q":"What if the client has Weak ties to India?","a":"Employment letter, business proof, property, family dependencies"},{"q":"Why is Weak ties to India a problem?","a":"No employment, assets, or family obligations documented."},{"q":"What if the client has Insufficient funds?","a":"Bank history, ITR, sponsor letter with host support"},{"q":"Why is Insufficient funds a problem?","a":"Cannot credibly fund trip or recent large deposits unexplained."}],"compliance":["Client service agreement on file before submission","Never guarantee visa approval","Separate consultancy and visa fees","Do not advise working in Australia on visitor visa"],"proTips":["Select correct stream at application","Personalise cover letter to visit purpose","For family visits, collect sponsor Form 1149 if Sponsored Family stream","Show employment leave letter for salaried applicants","Keep